name: Unidentified_Twi%27lek_(Umbaran%27s_Court)
content: A Twi'lek served in the court of Imperial Sub-Administrator Sly Moore. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, the Twi'lek and the rest of Moore's court plotted to assassinate the Sith Lord Darth Vader by hiring the assassin droid IG-88 and provided the bounty hunter with a datacard that contained the details of Vader's armor. Sometime later, Moore gathered the court in Administrative Temple Garden 313A on the planet Coruscant. Whilst in the garden, the court were approached by IG-88, who had failed to kill Vader and wanted to terminate their agreement. Vader then appeared and cut down the droid, and the court fled into a nearby temple where Vader ultimately defeated them.
